data.description: Welcome Home! This well maintained and affordable 2 bedroom Ranch is a commuter's dream and located in the sought after town of BOW! Minimal upkeep with a metal roof and a new Buderus boiler and hot water heater installed in 2021! Flexible floor plan with an updated kitchen and bath, hardwood floors throughout, large bedrooms, bright living room with fireplace, detached garage, and a walkout basement to your private yard with patio and fire pit for summer fun! Plenty of storage space in the walk-up attic and workshop in the lower level. All of this on over half an acre! Walking distance to park and sports fields. Wired for a generator and the property is lined with an underground dog fence. Delayed showings until the Open Houses this Saturday 2/11 and Sunday 2/12 11:00-1:00 . Offer deadline Monday 2/13/23 by 5:00 p.m.
